00:40:24,121 --> 00:40:26,522
But by stripping away these weapons,

766
00:40:27,223 --> 00:40:28,164
it made him feel maybe,

767
00:40:29,100 --> 00:40:31,334
a little bit different, more vulnerable in a way.

