00:40:32,262 --> 00:40:35,023
But at the same time, we wanted to replace those weapons

769
00:40:35,063 --> 00:40:36,444
with another iconic weapon.

770
00:40:36,744 --> 00:40:39,145
So this is why we decided to create an axe,

771
00:40:39,705 --> 00:40:41,886
which is a little bit more,

772
00:40:42,106 --> 00:40:44,767
it fits a little bit better within the Norse mythology

773
00:40:45,007 --> 00:40:45,987
that we were moving onto.

774
00:40:46,608 --> 00:40:53,110
