00:41:44,246 --> 00:41:45,987
and hit the enemies and come back automatically.

794
00:41:46,968 --> 00:41:49,890
So it wasn't until the breakthrough for the axe

795
00:41:50,191 --> 00:41:52,292
was definitely being able to throw it

796
00:41:52,692 --> 00:41:53,913
and being able to summon it back.

797
00:41:54,054 --> 00:41:57,016
And I mean that completely ties into the fantasy of Thor,

798
00:41:57,136 --> 00:41:58,517
you know, the Norse myth.

799
00:41:58,617 --> 00:42:00,659
So once we did that,

