00:45:56,513 --> 00:45:59,915
And having this direction of trying to make things

877
00:45:59,955 --> 00:46:01,215
more relatable and grounded,

878
00:46:01,756 --> 00:46:03,537
what better way than to get him in

879
00:46:04,077 --> 00:46:05,798
to try to do the moves for us?

880
00:46:06,398 --> 00:46:09,400
So he would lay out, his performance would give us

881
00:46:11,281 --> 00:46:13,562
80 to 90% of the way so that we can then take

