00:47:37,125 --> 00:47:38,886
what kind of personality he has,

907
00:47:39,607 --> 00:47:40,928
what type of movement he does.

908
00:47:41,508 --> 00:47:42,989
So we really got him involved

909
00:47:43,250 --> 00:47:45,892
as almost like one of the members of the animation team

910
00:47:46,332 --> 00:47:48,134
so that he would truly understand the character.

911
00:47:48,574 --> 00:47:49,775
So that it wasn't just about,

